Package it.polimi.ingsw.networking

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConnectionHandlerReceiverDelegate
    Delegator interface used to receive messages through the network and implemented by ClientSocket and Server classes.
    ConnectionHandlerSenderDelegate
    Delegator interface used to send messages through the network and implemented by ClientSocket and Server classes.
    WaitingRoomObserver
    Class implemented by a server to interact with a WaitingRoom
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Client
    Abstract class that will be reimplemented in ClientSocket and ClientRMI.
    Server
    Main class of the game server.
    ServerConnectionHandler
    Abstract superclass of Server's connectionHandlers for both RMI and Socket connections.
    WaitingRoom
    The game Waiting Room, used to start a new game when the minimum number users is available.
